<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="credibility-intro fade-up">
      <h2>Archway Works Exclusively With Independent Insurance Agencies</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="credibility-grid">
      <div class="credibility-card fade-up">
        <div class="credibility-icon orange">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26"><path d="M19.14 12.94c.04-.3.06-.61.06-.94 0-.32-.02-.64-.07-.94l2.03-1.58c.18-.14.23-.41.12-.61l-1.92-3.32c-.12-.22-.37-.29-.59-.22l-2.39.96c-.5-.38-1.03-.7-1.62-.94l-.36-2.54c-.04-.24-.24-.41-.48-.41h-3.84c-.24 0-.43.17-.47.41l-.36 2.54c-.59.24-1.13.57-1.62.94l-2.39-.96c-.22-.08-.47 0-.59.22L2.74 8.87c-.12.21-.08.47.12.61l2.03 1.58c-.05.3-.07.62-.07.94s.02.64.07.94l-2.03 1.58c-.18.14-.23.41-.12.61l1.92 3.32c.12.22.37.29.59.22l2.39-.96c.5.38 1.03.7 1.62.94l.36 2.54c.05.24.24.41.48.41h3.84c.24 0 .44-.17.47-.41l.36-2.54c.59-.24 1.13-.56 1.62-.94l2.39.96c.22.08.47 0 .59-.22l1.92-3.32c.12-.22.07-.47-.12-.61l-2.01-1.58zM12 15.6c-1.98 0-3.6-1.62-3.6-3.6s1.62-3.6 3.6-3.6 3.6 1.62 3.6 3.6-1.62 3.6-3.6 3.6z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>We Know Your Stack</h4>
        <p>AMS platforms, carrier portals, agency management workflows &mdash; we don&rsquo;t need a primer on how your business operates. We&rsquo;ve seen inside hundreds of agencies and we know exactly where the gaps tend to hide.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="credibility-card fade-up">
        <div class="credibility-icon blue">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>We Know What Carriers Are Looking For</h4>
        <p>Cybersecurity requirements from carriers aren&rsquo;t slowing down. We track what&rsquo;s changing and build our work around what actually matters for your risk posture and your renewals.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="credibility-card fade-up">
        <div class="credibility-icon orange">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26"><path d="M22.7 19l-9.1-9.1c.9-2.3.4-5-1.5-6.9-2-2-5-2.4-7.4-1.3L9 6 6 9 1.6 4.7C.4 7.1.9 10.1 2.9 12.1c1.9 1.9 4.6 2.4 6.9 1.5l9.1 9.1c.4.4 1 .4 1.4 0l2.3-2.3c.5-.4.5-1.1.1-1.4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>We Fix What We Find</h4>
        <p>We&rsquo;re not an audit firm that hands you a report and disappears. Archway handles IT, cybersecurity, digital marketing, and AI &mdash; so when we find something, we can fix it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .credibility-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .credibility-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .credibility-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .credibility-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
    border-color: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.3);
  }

  .credibility-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .credibility-icon svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
  }

  .credibility-icon.orange {
    background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.12);
  }
  .credibility-icon.orange svg {
    fill: var(--orange);
  }

  .credibility-icon.blue {
    background: rgba(41, 63, 80, 0.12);
  }
  .credibility-icon.blue svg {
    fill: var(--blue);
  }

  .credibility-card h4 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .credibility-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .credibility-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
